    "title": "Bekendtgørelse af bilag af 11. oktober 2002 til protokol af 2. november 1973 vedrørende indgriben på det åbne hav ved forurening af havet med andre stoffer end olie",
    "documentTypeId": "220",
    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "BKI nr 12 af 26/06/2008",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><p class=\"Titel2\">Bekendtgørelse af bilag af 11. oktober 2002 til protokol af 2. november 1973 vedrørende indgriben på det åbne hav ved forurening af havet med andre stoffer end olie</p>\r\n      <p class=\"Indledning2\">Den 11. oktober 2002 vedtog Den Internationale Sø­farts­organisation (IMO) ved resolution MEPC 100(48) en revision af den liste over stoffer, der skal vedhæftes som bilag til protokollen af 2. november 1973 vedrørende indgriben på det åbne hav ved forurening af havet med andre stoffer end olie, jf. bkg. nr. 113 af 26. september 1988 og bkg. nr. 24 af 23. august 2001, Lovtidende C.</p>\r\n      <p class=\"Indledning2\">Bilagets ordlyd er som følger:</p>\r\n      <p class=\"Tekst2\">\r\n        <div>\r\n          <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n            <table class=\"Maintable\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"SchultzColumns: 36 36 36 239 20 36 36 36 239;\" width=\"713\">\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td align=\"Right\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Oversættelse</span></div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Annex</span></div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td align=\"Right\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Bilag</span></div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td align=\"Center\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">LIST OF SUBSTANCES REFERRED TO IN PARAGRAPH 2(a) OF ARTICLE I OF THE 1973 INTERVEN- TION PROTOCOL</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td align=\"Center\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">LISTE OVER STOFFER I HENHOLD TIL ARTIKEL I, STK. 2(a) I 1973-INTERVENTIONSPROTOKOLLEN</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Any of the following products are subject to the 1973 Intervention Protocol if they are either carried on board a ship as cargo or are residues of such products previously carried:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Ethvert af de følgende produkter er omfattet af 1973-Interventionsprotokollen, hvis de enten føres ombord på et skib som fragt eller er restprodukter af sådanne produkter, som tidligere er ført:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"4\" width=\"346\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Oils</span>, as defined in Annex I to the International Convention for the Prevention of Pollution from Ships, 1973, as modified by the Protocol of 1978 relating there­to (MARPOL 73/78), as amended, when carried in bulk, including those listed in Appendix I with the exception of crude oil, fuel oil, diesel oil and lubricating oil which are covered by the 1969 Intervention Convention;</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Olier</span>, som defineret i Bilag I til den internationale konvention om forebyggelse af forurening fra skibe af 1973, ændret ved protokol af 1978 (MARPOL 73/78), med senere ændringer, når disse føres i bulk, inklusive de olier, der er nævnt i Tillæg I, med undtagelse af råolie, brændselsolie, dieselolie og smøreolie, som er omfattet af 1969-Interventionskonventionen;</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Noxious Liquid Substances</span>, as defined in Annex II to MARPOL 73/78, as amended, when carried in bulk, and identified:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Giftige flydende stoffer</span>, som defineret i Bilag II til MARPOL 73/78 med senere ændringer, når de føres i bulk, og er identificeret:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">as Pollution Category A or B, in: </div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">som forureningskategori A eller B i:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Chapter 17 of the International Bulk Chemical Code (IBC Code); or</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Kapitel 17 i IMO's internationale kode for bygning og udrustning af skibe til transport af farlige kemiske produkter i bulk (IBC-koden), eller</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Lists 1 to 4 of MEPC.2/Circulars, issued annually in December; or </div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Liste 1-4 i MEPC.2/Cirkulærer, som udsendes årligt i december måned, eller</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">in the composite list of GESAMP Haz­ard Profiles, issued periodically as BLG Circulars, with either:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"2\" width=\"275\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">i GESAMPs samleliste over risikoprofiler, som udsendes regelmæssigt som BLG-cirkulærer, med enten:</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">a 2 in column B and XX in col­umn E; or </div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.1</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">et 2-tal i spalte B og XX i spalte E, eller</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">XXX in column E; </div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">.2</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">XXX i spalte E;</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Harmful substances</span>, in packaged form, as defined in Annex III to MARPOL 73/78, as amended, and which have been identified as Severe Marine Pollutants (PP) in the International Maritime Dangerous Goods Code (IMDG Code) or which meet the criteria for such as defined in the IMDG Code;</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">3</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Skadelige stoffer</span> i emballeret form, som defineret i Bilag III til MARPOL 73/78 med senere ændringer, og som er blevet identificeret som særligt farlige marineforurenende stoffer (PP) i IMOs internationale kode for transport af farligt gods til søs (IMDG-koden) eller som opfylder kriterierne derfor i IMDG-koden;</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Radioactive material</span>, transported in type B or type C packages, or as fissile material, or under special arrangements, as covered by the provisions of class 7 of the IMDG Code; and</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">4</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Radioaktivt materiale</span>, som transporteres i type B- eller type C-emballage, eller som fissilt materiale, eller under særlige ordninger, som er omfattet af bestemmelserne i klasse 7 i IMDG-koden; og</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"239\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">5</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Liquefied gases</span>, identified in chapter 19 of the International Code for the Construction and Equipment of Ships Carrying Liquefied Gases in Bulk, 1983 (IGC Code), as amended, when carried in bulk, and the products for which preliminary suitable conditions for the carriage have been prescribed by the Admin­istration and port administrations involved in accordance with paragraph 1.1.6 of the IGC Code.</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td width=\"20\"> </td>\r\n                <td width=\"36\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">5</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n                <td colspan=\"3\" width=\"311\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\"><span class=\"Bold\">Flydende gas</span>, som er identificeret i kapitel 19 i IMO's internationale kode fra 1983 for bygning og udrustning af skibe til transport af flydende gas i bulk (IGC-koden) med senere ændringer, når de transporteres i bulk, og de produkter for hvilke passende foreløbige betingelser for transport er foreskrevet af Administrationen og de relevante havnemyndigheder i henholde til afsnit 1.1.6 i IGC-koden.</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"9\" style=\"padding-left: 0.191cm; padding-right: 0.191cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" width=\"713\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"9\" style=\"padding-left: 0.191cm; padding-right: 0.191cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" width=\"713\"> </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n              <tr>\r\n                <td colspan=\"9\" style=\"padding-left: 0.191cm; padding-right: 0.191cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" width=\"713\">\r\n                  <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Det reviderede bilag trådte i henhold til protokollens artikel III, stk. 7, i kraft den 22. juni 2004.</div>\r\n                </td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n            </table>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </p>\r\n      <p class=\"Tekst2\">\r\n        <div></div>\r\n      </p><DIV CLASS=GIVET ID=\"GIVET\"><FONT SIZE=\"3\"><P CLASS=GIVET ALIGN=\"CENTER\"><I>Udenrigsministeriet, den 26. juni 2008</I></P><P CLASS=SIGN1 ALIGN=\"CENTER\">Per Stig Møller</P><P CLASS=SIGN2 ALIGN=\"RIGHT\"></P></FONT></DIV>",
